om\": 2490, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, this upside momentum appears exhausted, with a pending sell signal on the Moving Average Convergence Divergence (MACD).\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2727, \"end\": 2738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limit_of_a_sequence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1799423064528486e-21, \"text\": \"Convergence\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limit_of_a_sequence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limit_of_a_sequence\"}, {\"begin\": 2739, \"end\": 2749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Divergence\", \"score\": 0.6579221662097396, \"rank\": 0.5199366298312766, \"text\": \"Divergence\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Divergence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Divergence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarly, the Relative Strength Index (RSI) is southbound and could break below its ascending trendline if selling pressure increases.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2774, \"end\": 2803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Relative_strength_index\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Relative Strength Index (RSI)\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Relative_strength_index\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Relative_strength_index\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If both the MACD and RSI break below their supporting trendlines, the Neiro price could extend the fall.\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 3000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2917, \"end\": 2920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Repetitive_strain_injury\", \"score\": 0.9926803729150783, \"rank\": 0.007367754882820502, \"text\": \"RSI\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Repetitive_strain_injury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Repetitive_strain_injury\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Notably, even the MACD's histograms are paling out, suggesting 